# Israeli accessibility — IS 5568 (dashboard)

Comply with **Israeli Standard IS 5568** (WCAG 2.1 Level AA) for all `dashboard/**` UI changes.

## Non-negotiables

- Semantic HTML: native buttons/links; one `<main>`; proper headings; `aria-current` on nav.
- Keyboard: Tab/Enter/Space; visible `:focus-visible`; skip link to `#main-content` (map) or `#legal-main` (legal pages).
- Forms: visible labels; `aria-invalid` + errors; `role="alert"` for dynamic errors.
- Images: meaningful `alt`; icon-only controls need `aria-label`.
- Color: 4.5:1 text contrast; do not rely on color alone; high-contrast toggle must remain available.
- Motion: respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.
- Language: `lang="en"` on `<html>`; legal/visible copy in English; Hebrew only in SEO `keywords` meta.
- Legal: maintain `/accessibility` with coordinator **Amir Labay** — `amirlabay+support@gmail.com`.

